'''舟·沃頓'''（Jo Walton，{{bd|1964年|12月1日}}）<ref>[http://www.theguardian.com/books/2012/oct/02/jo-walton-among-others-interview Jo Walton's Among Others: 'It's a mythologisation of part of my life'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/books/2012/oct/02/jo-walton-among-others-interview |date=20210314182123 }} at [[the_Guardian|the Guardian]]; by [[David_Barnett|David Barnett]]; published October 2, 2012; retrieved November 4, 2013</ref>是[[英國|英國]]－[[加拿大|加拿大]][[奇幻小說|奇幻小說]]和[[科幻小說|科幻小說]]作家、[[詩人|詩人]]。她在2002年贏得[[約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎|約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎]]，她在2004年獲得[[世界奇幻獎|世界奇幻獎]]，她是2008年[[普羅米修斯獎|普羅米修斯獎]]得主。她的小說《Lifelode》榮獲2010年（Mythopoeic）[[神話獎|神話獎]]。她的小說《我不屬於他們》贏得2011年[[星雲獎|星雲獎]]最佳小說獎和2012年[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳小說獎<ref>[http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/09/announcing-the-2012-hugo-award-winners Announcing the 2012 Hugo Award Winners] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/09/announcing-the-2012-hugo-award-winners |date=20150425075836 }} at Tor.com, published September 2, 2012, retrieved September 2, 2012]</ref> <ref>[http://www.locusmag.com/News/2012/05/2011-nebula-awards-winners/ 2011 Nebula Award Winners] {{Wayback|url=http://www.locusmag.com/News/2012/05/2011-nebula-awards-winners/ |date=20170713162304 }} at Locus Online News, published May 19, 2012, retrieved May 20, 2012</ref>，也入圍[[世界奇幻獎|世界奇幻獎]]。

